    # game/areas/ruinedshelter.rpy:1894
    old "The beaten ground is marked with paw prints of dusk foxes, but is turning into a grassland. The soil is unremarkable - the spare bushes have little competition. \n\nThere’s a few spots where the grass grew unusually tall, and once you take a closer look, you realize those are weak stems of barley. They could be brought here by birds from one of the villages, or dropped by a human visitor. "
