    new ""

    # game/areas/ruinedshelter.rpy:2001
    old "There’s nothing around that could be easily turned into a meal, at least not one edible for you. The mushrooms require long preparations, an access to a fireplace, and cooking instruments, while the bugs would need to be caught first, what’s not an easy task, especially without a trap. \n\nThe more convenient foods, such as the fruits or nuts, are already devoured or hidden by the dusk foxes, birds, and squirrels. "
